data.title: K1 Speed Indoor Go Karts Anaheim
data.meta_description: K1 Speed Anaheim belongs to a chain of indoor racing centers featuring electric go-karting for all ages and skill levels, plus great food. Anaheim go-kart racing tracks are professionally designed, fully enclosed for racing in rain or shine, and well maintained. The most popular attraction is Arrive & Drive race option where up to 12 racers at a time take to the track to race

data.text: K1 Speed Anaheim belongs to a chain of indoor racing centers featuring electric go-karting for all ages and skill levels, plus great food. Anaheim go-kart racing tracks are professionally designed, fully enclosed for racing in rain or shine, and well maintained. The most popular attraction is Arrive & Drive race option where up to 12 racers at a time take to the track to race against the clock.
